{"id": "art-151", "label": "Art. 151", "title": "Art. 151: Livrarea supravegheată", "slug": "art-151", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:\nblack'>Art. 151: Livrarea supravegheat&#259; </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1851240035\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2403\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1851240035\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)Livrarea supravegheat&#259; poate fi autorizat&#259;,\nprin ordonan&#355;&#259;, de c&#259;tre procurorul care supravegheaz&#259; sau\nefectueaz&#259; urm&#259;rirea penal&#259;, la solicitarea institu&#355;iilor\nsau organelor competente, cu sau f&#259;r&#259; sustragerea ori substituirea\ntotal&#259; sau par&#355;ial&#259; a bunurilor care fac obiectul livr&#259;rii.</span><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>(2)<b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:\nnormal'>Livrarea supravegheat&#259; poate fi autorizat&#259; numai în\nurm&#259;toarele cazuri:</b></span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_27630617\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2402\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_27630617\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>a)dac&#259; descoperirea sau arestarea persoanelor\nimplicate în transportul ilegal de droguri, substan&#355;e dopante, arme,\nobiecte furate, materiale explozive &#351;i precursori de explozivi\nrestric&#355;iona&#355;i, nucleare, alte materiale radioactive, sume de bani\n&#351;i alte obiecte care rezult&#259; din activit&#259;&#355;i ilicite ori\nobiecte utilizate în scopul comiterii de infrac&#355;iuni nu ar putea fi\nf&#259;cut&#259; în alt mod sau ar presupune dificult&#259;&#355;i deosebite ce\nar prejudicia ancheta ori un pericol pentru siguran&#355;a persoanelor sau a\nunor bunuri de valoare;</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='color:black'>b)dac&#259;\ndescoperirea ori dovedirea infrac&#355;iunilor s&#259;vâr&#351;ite în\nleg&#259;tur&#259; cu livrarea de transporturi ilegale sau suspecte ar fi\nimposibil&#259; ori foarte dificil&#259; în alt mod.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1726194330\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2401\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1726194330\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2<sup>1</sup>)<b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'>Livrarea\nsupravegheat&#259; poate fi realizat&#259; pe teritoriul &#355;&#259;rii numai\ndac&#259; procurorul care supravegheaz&#259; sau efectueaz&#259; urm&#259;rirea\npenal&#259; se asigur&#259; c&#259; autorit&#259;&#355;ile care au, potrivit\nlegii, atribu&#355;ii în leg&#259;tur&#259; cu verificarea sau supravegherea\nintr&#259;rii, circula&#355;iei sau ie&#351;irii de pe teritoriul\n&#355;&#259;rii a bunurilor vizate:</b></span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1401682381\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2400\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1401682381\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>a)p&#259;streaz&#259; confiden&#355;ialitatea\nactivit&#259;&#355;ilor desf&#259;&#351;urate;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_367898055\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2399\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_367898055\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>b)garanteaz&#259; supravegherea permanent&#259; a\ntransportului ilegal sau suspect.</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_918635059\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2398\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_918635059\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)<b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'>În situa&#355;ia\nîn care livrarea supravegheat&#259; presupune activit&#259;&#355;i\ntransfrontaliere, aceasta poate fi realizat&#259; numai dac&#259; procurorul\ncare supravegheaz&#259; sau efectueaz&#259; urm&#259;rirea penal&#259; ia\nm&#259;suri &#351;i se asigur&#259; ca autorit&#259;&#355;ile statelor\ntranzitate:</b></span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_625162515\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2397\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_625162515\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>a)s&#259; fie de acord cu intrarea pe teritoriul acestora a\ntransportului ilegal sau suspect &#351;i cu ie&#351;irea acestuia de pe\nteritoriul statului;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_91312530\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2396\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_91312530\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>b)s&#259; garanteze faptul c&#259; transportul ilegal sau\nsuspect este supravegheat permanent de c&#259;tre autorit&#259;&#355;ile\ncompetente;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1942494078\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2395\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1942494078\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>c)s&#259; garanteze faptul c&#259; procurorul, organele de\npoli&#355;ie sau alte autorit&#259;&#355;i de stat competente sunt\nîn&#351;tiin&#355;ate în ceea ce prive&#351;te rezultatul urm&#259;ririi penale\nîmpotriva persoanelor acuzate de infrac&#355;iuni care au constituit obiectul\nmetodei speciale de cercetare la care se face referire la alin. (1).</span><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>(4)Dispozi&#355;iile alin. (3) nu se\naplic&#259; în cazul în care un tratat interna&#355;ional la care România este\nparte are dispozi&#355;ii contrare.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1124302040\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2394\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1124302040\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(5)<b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'>Pentru fiecare\nlivrare supravegheat&#259; procurorul emite câte o ordonan&#355;&#259;, care\ntrebuie s&#259; cuprind&#259;, pe lâng&#259; men&#355;iunile prev&#259;zute la\nart. 286 alin. (2):</b></span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1544922735\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2393\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1544922735\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>a)numele suspectului sau inculpatului, dac&#259; sunt\ncunoscute;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1443118137\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2392\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1443118137\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>b)motivele concrete care justific&#259; m&#259;sura;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1446395757\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2391\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1446395757\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>c)indicarea bunurilor care fac obiectul livr&#259;rii\nsupravegheate &#351;i a dovezilor din care rezult&#259; caracterul ilicit al\nacestora, a bunurilor care urmeaz&#259; a fi sustrase sau substituite, precum\n&#351;i a bunurilor care urmeaz&#259; a le înlocui pe acestea, dup&#259; caz;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_159337839\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2390\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_159337839\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>d)timpul &#351;i locul efectu&#259;rii livr&#259;rii sau,\ndup&#259; caz, itinerarul ce urmeaz&#259; a fi parcurs în vederea\nefectu&#259;rii livr&#259;rii, dac&#259; acestea sunt cunoscute;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1682640849\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2389\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1682640849\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>e)modalit&#259;&#355;ile în care va fi efectuat&#259;\nsupravegherea;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_47785574\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2388\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_47785574\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>f)datele de identificare a persoanelor autorizate s&#259;\nsupravegheze livrarea.</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>(6)Livrarea supravegheat&#259; este\npus&#259; în aplicare de c&#259;tre poli&#355;ie sau de alt&#259; autoritate\ncompetent&#259;. Procurorul stabile&#351;te, coordoneaz&#259; &#351;i\ncontroleaz&#259; modul de punere în aplicare a livr&#259;rii supravegheate.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>(7)Punerea în aplicare a\nlivr&#259;rii supravegheate nu constituie infrac&#355;iune.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_837532505\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2387\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_837532505\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(8)Organele prev&#259;zute la alin. (6) au obliga&#355;ia\nde a întocmi, la finalizarea livr&#259;rii supravegheate pe teritoriul\nRomâniei, un proces-verbal cu privire la activit&#259;&#355;ile\ndesf&#259;&#351;urate, pe care îl înainteaz&#259; procurorului.</span><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>"}